Definition: done or made using whatever is available
Example: crossed the river on improvised bridges; the survivors used jury-rigged fishing gear; the rock served as a makeshift hammer
Synonyms: jury-rigged, makeshift, noun, act, done, or, made, using, whatever, is, available, crossed, the, river, on, bridges, survivors, used, fishing, gear, rock, served, as, a, hammer
Category: adj.all
